\citation{he2016deep}
\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {FedProTrack pipeline (one federation round).} Module~1 (blue): each client computes a class-conditional fingerprint $\phi _k$ in a single pass ($\mathcal  {O}(dL)$ bytes, no training). Module~2 (green): the server performs OT spectral clustering with eigengap-based concept-count selection and matches clusters to a persistent memory bank. Module~3 (orange): clients receive concept-matched models and perform local training; per-concept FedAvg aggregation follows. Module~4 (purple): empirical-Bayes shrinkage interpolates between concept-level and global models based on estimated SNR. Communication overhead: $2.1\times $ FedAvg.}}{6}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:pipeline}{{3}{6}{\textbf {FedProTrack pipeline (one federation round).} Module~1 (blue): each client computes a class-conditional fingerprint $\phi _k$ in a single pass ($\mathcal {O}(dL)$ bytes, no training). Module~2 (green): the server performs OT spectral clustering with eigengap-based concept-count selection and matches clusters to a persistent memory bank. Module~3 (orange): clients receive concept-matched models and perform local training; per-concept FedAvg aggregation follows. Module~4 (purple): empirical-Bayes shrinkage interpolates between concept-level and global models based on estimated SNR. Communication overhead: $2.1\times $ FedAvg}{figure.3}{}}
